plot: Vic turns in his badge a week early and sets out to find and kill Shane and his wife. However, Ronnie is benched after Claudette shuts down the Strike Team. Meanwhile, Aceveda finds out more disturbing information about Cruz Pezuela.

Mara left something,leaving a trail behind. Ronnie asks for new blood for the strike-team to be functional again. The investigation into Cruz Pezuela takes new turns for Olivia and Councilman Aceveda. Corinne is lead into friction, doubting Vic's good intentions to send Shane's family out of the country.—ANDUG8
